_sText:
**Information:**
================
I made this map from scratch with some help by looking on other maps, using some prefabs and getting feedback.

If you like it and wanna thank me please give it some rating and also please comment.

Please do not take credit of making this map your self and also please do not remove the "map by mooni" text ingame.

**Whats new in v4:**
========================

- Changed posision on some boxes.

- Locked the "Death pit" button so you have to unlock it over medic.

- Added glowing colors over the buttons outside armory.

- Removed some uninportant information.

- Moved the "map by mooni" text to a little room outside the map.

- Small texture fixes.

- Made the laser jump a bit easier.

- I was going to give out the code to the teleport behind the cells but i forgot how it worked.. (I havent been using source sdk for about 4 months.)

**Whats new in v3:**
========================

- Added more boxes.

- Map name change from **jb_ggaming** to **jb_boxes**.

- Added some new secrets in cells.

- Made it impossible to "lock in" someone. _(Added vents or secrets so you allways can get out of somewhere.)_

- Added a button in armory to unluck the outside trigger to armory door.

- Some small fixes with cell doors.

**Whats new in v2:**
======================

- Added boxes. _(For lava day and more interesting war days.)_

- Some Texture fixes in pool and fotball.

- Benches in fotball.

- A little wire in the main room.

- Increased deagle toss length.

**This map contains:**
======================

- Cells and Armory. :o

- Isolation cell.

- Medic.

- Fotball.

- Pool.

- Individual working showers.

- Death pit.

- Fountain.

- Deagle toss room.

- Cage hole. _(instead of big cage)_

- Secrets.

Please give me as much feedback as possible!
============================================

This is my third map i ever made and it's the first one im happy with.
I worked on the first version of it for around 120 hours and it would make my day if i got some constructive feedback.

Please give me as much feedback as possible!
============================================
